Oviedo Health & Senior Expo Location: Oviedo Mall, Oviedo FL Join us for a fun and informative event celebrating seniors! There will be free health screenings, bingo, workshops, free samples, shopping opportunities, community services, and more. Learn about senior living, retirement, holistic health, nutrition, travel and leisure, and health and wellness. Parking and admission are both free, so bring a friend! For more information, call 386-860-0092 or visit Buckler Promotions’s website. View Map & Details

Back 2 School Bash Location: Gemini Springs, Debary Florida Who Qualifies for a FREE Backpack? Children (K-5 – 12th Grade) with at least 1 parent who has served Parents can be Active Duty, Reservists or Veteran’s of ANY military branch MUST pre-register at our website and be able to pick up at the event. There is limited space so sign up quickly! … Operation: Care 4 R Troops will be offering FREE backpacks filled with school supplies for our Military kids! Check out Website or our Facebook page for more information! FREE filled Backpacks! Game Giveaways! All you need to do is show up during the allotted time to pick up your bag. You’ll need your military ID or DD-214 for proof to show on the day of pick up! We’ll have tons of fun planned-so watch our Facebook page for more details or our website. Back to School Bash! Saturday, August 8, 2015 Gemini Springs Park, Debary, FL Pavilion #1 by the playground! View Map & Details

1Voice Talent Show Season 3 Location: Satellite Center, Orlando Florida 1Voice is a singing competition where singers compete for a chance to win their very own single done by Maximum Entertainment Group. Back to School Bash Location: New Life Church of Orlando, Ocoee FL New Life Church of Orlando, COGIC is excited to host the Inaugrual Back to School Bash on 8/8/15.
